OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FWords by ITV News' Lucy L. Middleton
OL,8,FThere is renewed speculation that the
OL,9,FUS may try to seize Kharg Island in
OL,10,Fthe Persian Gulf.
OL,12,FMultiple reports in US media suggest
OL,13,Fsenior White House officials are
OL,14,Fconsidering an operation to take over
OL,15,Fthe coral island, which sits 16 miles
OL,16,Ffrom the southwestern shore of
OL,17,Fmainland Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
