OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774455107
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,F"The United States Central Command
OL,7,Fexecuted one of the most powerful
OL,8,Fbombing raids in the History of the
OL,9,FMiddle East and totally obliterated
OL,10,Fevery MILITARY target in Iran's crown
OL,11,Fjewel, Kharg Island," Trump posted on
OL,12,FMarch 13.
OL,14,F"I have chosen NOT to wipe out the Oil
OL,15,FInfrastructure on the Island. However,
OL,16,Fshould Iran, or anyone else, do
OL,17,Fanything to interfere with the Free
OL,18,Fand Safe Passage of Ships through the
OL,19,FStrait of Hormuz, I will immediately
OL,20,Freconsider this decision."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
