OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FUS Central Command claimed it had
OL,7,Fdestroyed naval mine storage
OL,8,Ffacilities and missile storage bunkers
OL,9,Fin the attack.
OL,11,FIran's semi-official Fars news agency
OL,12,Fsaid the strikes had caused no damage
OL,13,Fto oil infrastructure, but an air
OL,14,Fdefence facility, naval base, airport
OL,15,Fcontrol tower and helicopter hangar
OL,16,Fbelonging to an offshore oil company
OL,17,Fhad been targeted.
OL,19,FWhat impact could a further attack
OL,20,Fhave?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
