OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FSeizing Kharg could give the US a
OL,7,Fbargaining tool against Iran in the
OL,8,Fbattle to fully reopen the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz, experts have said, as
OL,10,Fdisrupting oil exports would cause
OL,11,Feconomic devastation to the country.
OL,13,FHowever, it would also significantly
OL,14,Fescalate the ongoing conflict, with
OL,15,FIran vowing to avenge any action taken
OL,16,Fon the island.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
