PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774455107
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FA military source told IRGC-affiliated
OL,7,FTasnim News the regime would block
OL,8,Fother vital waterways such as the Bab
OL,9,Fal-Mandab Strait and the Red Sea, if
OL,10,FKharg were invaded.
