OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FThe near closure of the Strait of
OL,7,FHormuz has seen oil prices surge to
OL,8,Fmore than $100 a barrel continuously
OL,9,Fsince the war began, with the world's
OL,10,Femergency oil system releasing a
OL,11,Frecord 400 million barrels to combat
OL,12,Fthe spike.
OL,14,FIran also threatened to target energy
OL,15,Fand water facilities belonging to
OL,16,Fneighbouring countries in the Gulf
OL,17,Fwhen Trump issued the regime a 48-hour
OL,18,Fdeadline to reopen the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz at the weekend.
OL,21,FWhat has the White House said?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
