OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774455107
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FTrump told reporters on Tuesday that
OL,7,FIran has agreed to "never have a
OL,8,Fnuclear weapon" and said the countries
OL,9,Fare "in negotiations right now", even
OL,10,Fthough the Pentagon is in the process
OL,11,Fof deploying two units that will add
OL,12,Fabout 5,000 Marines and thousands of
OL,13,Fsailors to the region.
OL,15,FThe move - which will supplement some
OL,16,F50,000 troops already in the region -
OL,17,Fis designed to give the US president
OL,18,F"max flexibility" on what to do next,
OL,19,Fa person with knowledge of the
OL,20,Fdeployment told AP.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
