OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FIt has raised speculation that the US
OL,7,Fmay try to seize Kharg Island or carry
OL,8,Fout an operation to remove enriched
OL,9,Furanium from inside Iran.
OL,11,FLess than a week ago, Trump declared
OL,12,Fthat the US could "take out" Kharg
OL,13,FIsland "anytime we want", telling
OL,14,Freporters at the White House on Friday
OL,15,Fthe land was "totally unprotected".
OL,17,FWhen asked about a planned invasion or
OL,18,Fblockade of Kharg, the White House's
OL,19,Fpress secretary said the US could
OL,20,Fattack the island "if the president
OL,21,Fgives the order".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
