OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774455107
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting it sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,F"The one claiming to be a global
OL,7,Fsuperpower would have already gotten
OL,8,Fout of this mess if it could. Don't
OL,9,Fdress up your defeat as an agreement.
OL,10,FYour era of empty promises has come to
OL,11,Fan end."
